verbose_text: Cluster 3 contains 8 drains for the pre-lockdown (d2, d16, d17, d19, d21, d22, d23 and d24) and 4 drains (d2, d17, d21 & d24) for the lockdown slots and the lowest water quality level was recorded in them in both phases, i.e. these comprise the ' most ' polluting group (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY).
